metadata.name: NEON TECHNOLYXE_ COSMOPOLITE SEA
metadata.description:
The Name of The Artwork is Cosmopolite Sea and was made for a solo show Exhitbition in Monterrey, Mexico. 
Made with Cinema 4d and Adobe the artwork seeks to represent the cosmopolite world of Monterrey and how it emerge by the sea of fashion, nightlife and modern buildings. 
(15529px  ×  12000px) 
-JPEG
-ready to print
